<div id="content">        <div class="spacer"></div>             <span id="shash-54261"><div class="post" id="post-54261">                    <h1><a href="http://trilema.com/2014/idiocy-without-borders-idiots-sans-frontieres/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Idiocy without borders / Idiots sans frontieres">Idiocy without borders / Idiots sans frontieres</a></h1>                        <div class="date">                                     Friday, 02 May, Year 6 d.Tr.&nbsp;|&nbsp;Author: <a href="http://trilema.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Mircea Popescu">Mircea Popescu</a>                                                        </div>

                        <div class="entry">
<p>(It all started as all good things start these days : on <a href="http://trilema.com/forum-logs-for-02-may-2014#1242303">irc</a>. <em>Bien sur</em>.)</p>
<h1><center>~ Part I ~</center></h1>
<blockquote><p><strong>tradingloser</strong> (42fef14c@gateway/web/freenode/ip.66.254.241.76) has joined #bitcoin-assets<br />
<strong>mircea_popescu</strong> !up tradingloser<br />
