<strong>mike_c</strong> If it makes you feel better, everyone who trades on those exchanges loses money.<sup><a href="#footnote_0_54261" id="identifier_0_54261" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="He has a point, you know.">i</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>tradingloser</strong> Okay.. so O guess I'm in a double whammy.. I suck at trading + on a site where people always lose money..<br />
<strong>mircea_popescu</strong> They're called play exchanges for a reason.</p>
